data.description: This spacious townhome has everything you need and more in a private GATED community. The first level features a bedroom with a full bath, perfect for guests or a home office. The second level has an open concept living area with a cozy fireplace, hardwood floors throughout, and a beautiful kitchen with solid surface countertops and stainless steel appliances. The two bedrooms upstairs each have their own full bath, so everyone has their own space.  This is located in a maintenance-free community, so you can spend your time enjoying your new home instead of worrying about yard work!
